<H3> <TI>   Foreign Minister, ICO Leader Discuss Cooperation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Foreign Minister, ICO Leader Discuss Cooperation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2106214694 Riyadh SPA in English 1923 GMT 21 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2106214694 </F>
<F P=104>  Riyadh SPA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Kuwait, June 21, SPA -- The Kuwaiti First Deputy 
Premier and Foreign Minister Shaykh Sabah al-Ahmad met here on 
Tuesday [21 June] with the secretary general of the Organization 
of Islamic Conference Dr Hamid Algabid who is currently visiting 
Kuwait. 
  During the meeting, they discussed cooperation between 
Kuwait 
and the ICO. 
  Shaykh Sabah also conferred today with the parliament 
speaker 
of Comoros Islands Mr Fernandez who is visiting Kuwait. 

</TEXT>

