<F P=100> Palestinian Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Police Turn 4 Murder Suspects Over to Israel </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Police Turn 4 Murder Suspects Over to Israel </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA2406043994 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 0400 GMT 24 
Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2406043994 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] For the first time, Palestinian forces in the 
autonomous zones have arrested four murder suspects and turned 
them over to Israel Police. The four, arrested by police in 
Jericho, are suspected of the brutal murder of a young 
Palestinian woman, Fatima 'Abd-al-Hamid, from the village of 
Baytuniya, near Ramallah. The suspects, from the al-Jalazun 
refugee camp, escaped to Jericho and, at the request of Israel 
Police, were extradited. 

</TEXT>

