  [Text] The national dialogue and the economic and political 
reforms [in the country] were on the agenda of the talks between 
Foreign Minister Mohamed Salah Dembri and U.S. officials. More 
details on Dembri's talks in the United States with Wahiba 
Benchihab: 
  [Benchihab] Mr. Dembri asserted yesterday at his meeting 
with 
