economic and political reforms under way in Algeria and is very 
interested in the process of the transitional period. 
  Mr. Dembri also reviewed, at a dinner given by the Senate 
Foreign Affairs Committee, the efforts of the Algerian 
authorities to broaden dialogue in the search for national 
concord and the outcome of his talks with U.S. officials. 

