<H3> <TI>   Acting Premier Inspects Food Storehouses </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Acting Premier Inspects Food Storehouses </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN2306210594 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
1700 GMT 23 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN2306210594 </F>
<F P=104>  Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Summary from poor reception] Acting Prime Minister Brother 
Muhammad Sa'id al-'Attar has visited al-Hudaydah Governorate and 
inspected storehouses of basic food and became acquainted with 
the food situation there. 
  Al-'Attar emphasized that measures should be taken to ensure 
that food regularly reaches the governorate and that monopoly of 
