<H3> <TI>   Damascus Declaration Ministers Conference Postponed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Damascus Declaration Ministers Conference Postponed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC2506204394 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1830 GMT 25 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2506204394 </F>
