<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 25 Jun (MENA) -- MENA has learned that the 
meeting of the Damascus Declaration countries' foreign 
ministers, which was to be held in Kuwait next Tuesday [28 June] 
has been postponed to a later date. 

</TEXT>

