of the Shamgar Commission. Dr. Sa'ib 'Urayqat said the Cave of 
the Patriarchs massacre was not perpetuated by one individual 
but rather stemmed from the settlement policy. He maintains, 
therefore, that the Israeli Government should bear the 
responsibility. 'Urayqat warned that the presence of the 
settlers in the territories is a time bomb which can go off any 
minute. 

