<H3> <TI>   Damascus Sit-In Shows Solidarity With Prisoners </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Damascus Sit-In Shows Solidarity With Prisoners </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN2606132194 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in 
Arabic 1115 GMT 26 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN2606132194 </F>
<F P=104>  Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Delegations from the Alliance of Palestinian Forces 
and other Palestinian popular organizations staged a sit-in at 
the headquarters of the International Committee of the Red Cross 
[ICRC] in Damascus today to show solidarity with the Palestinian 
prisoners and detainees held in Israeli occupation jails. 
  The delegations presented memorandums to the ICRC 
representative in Damascus addressed to the ICRC in Geneva and 
the UN secretary general asking them to intervene for the 
release of Palestinian prisoners and detainees and to ensure 
their right to express their views on all that concerns their 
cause, people, and homeland. 

</TEXT>

