<F P=100> ARAB AFRICA </F>
<F P=101> Algeria </F>
<H3> <TI>   Sifi Returns From Trip </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Sifi Returns From Trip </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2406163494 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 1600 
GMT 24 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2406163494 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Radio Algiers Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The head of government, Mokdad Sifi, returned to the 
homeland today after a 48-hour visit to France. 
  In a statement to APS, the head of government said that he 
was very happy with the result of his visits to Brussels and 
Paris. He said that he had gained European support and backing 
for the policy which is being pursued by the Algerian 
authorities in the political and economic fields. 

</TEXT>

