<F P=102> LD2506113594 Kuwait KUNA in Arabic 1026 GMT 25 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2506113594 </F>
<F P=104>  Kuwait KUNA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Aden, 25 Jun (KUNA) -- The southern Yemeni air 
defenses downed a northern Yemeni plane above the Shaykh 'Uthman 
area in the outskirts of Aden at midday today after its attempt 
to raid the area. 
  A KUNA correspondent in Aden saw the northern Yemeni MiG-21 
aircraft burning in flight over the central prison in the Shaykh 
'Uthman area. However, an official communique issued by the 
Defense Ministry in Aden affirmed that the Southern air defenses 
downed a northern Yemeni plane above Aden. 

</TEXT>

