<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] His Excellency 'Abd-al-'Aziz 'Abd-al-Ghani, 
Presidential Council member and envoy of His Excellency Yemeni 
President 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, arrived in the country this 
afternoon on a two-day visit to the sultanate. 
  In a statement to the Omani News Agency upon arrival, his 
