regional, Arab, and international arenas in light of the wisdom 
and awareness of his majesty, and the love he enjoys among the 
Yemeni people. 
  His excellency expressed pleasure for visiting the sultanate 
to meet with Omani officials. 
  He was received upon arrival by Qays Bin-'Abd-al-Mun'im 
al-Zawawi, deputy prime minister for financial and economic 
affairs. 

