BFN 

  [Text] Brother 'Abd-al-'Aziz 'Abd-al-Ghani, member of the 
Presidential Council, returned to Sanaa this afternoon, winding 
up a working visit to the sisterly Sultanate of Oman. During 
the visit, brother 'Abd-al-Ghani conveyed a message from brother 
