<H4>    South Claims Plane Downed, Tanks Destroyed </H4>

<F P=102> NC2706211094 Cairo MENA in Arabic 2030 GMT 27 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2706211094 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


