  [Text] Cairo, 27 Jun (MENA) -- A military source in Aden 
today said that southern forces downed one of several northern 
planes that were trying to bombard Aden's oil refineries. 
  In a statement faxed to MENA tonight, the source said that 
southern troops destroyed six tanks and killed, wounded, or 
captured hundreds of northern troops. 

